ISIQALILE inkonzo yesikhumbuzo kaLebo Monene sontweni iTembisa Christian Family Church enkonzweni yesikhumbuzo. Le nkonzo kuthiwa yenzelwe abangani kanye nozakwabo kaMonene abangakwazanga ukuya emngcwabeni wakhe obuseLimpopo ngempelasonto. UMonene wahlaselwa uphathina wakhe esemsebenzini esibhedlela iTembisa Provincial Tertiary ngesonto eledlule. UMsolwa wafika kulesi sibhedlela ehamba ngemoto yomsebenzi wapaka endaweni yabezimo eziphuthumayo. Uphathina wakhe oyiphoyisa wafika wamshayela ucingo ukuba babonane, ngesikhathi efika kuyena, lavulela ngenhlamvu lamdubula ngaphambi kokuba liphendule isibhamu lizame ukuzibulala nalo. Imibiko evelayo, ithi umsolwa uyalulama esibhedlela.  